nodes.text: Henia Kinalos was the daughter of Kinalos and his partner Tanne. She had at least two brothers.

Henia lived on Coruscant with her family around the time of the Galactic Civil War. She owned a stuffed toy felinx. During the Imperial Civil War that followed in the aftermath of the Second Battle of Coruscant in 10 ABY, the Kinalos home was occupied by Imperial Stormtroopers. Henia and the rest of her family were forced to flee, leaving many of their possessions behind. Her father, serving with the New Republic Army, later returned to his ruined home, clearing Imperial forces from it before abandoning it for good.
